Enochian magick is a system of ritual magick based mainly on the writings of Edward Kelly and John Dee. These 16th century authors claimed to have obtained their knowledge directly from angels, who revealed to them the secrets contained in the Book of Enoch.

Samuel Liddell MacGregor Mathers later discovered these works and included them into the Golden Dawn system of ceremonial magick.

Enochian principals and beliefs form an important part of the Crowley, Golden Dawn, and several other systems of magick. The books in this torrent will give the reader a good understanding of this branch of magick.
